      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ciclo di scansione                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-exe-ctr-001          .
       exe-exp-ybx-620.
           add       1                    to   w-exe-ctr-001          .
           if        w-exe-ctr-001        >    10
                     go to exe-exp-ybx-750.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test preliminari                            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-ybo-tbe-scg
                    (w-exe-ctr-001)       =    zero and
                     rf-ybo-tbe-asc
                    (w-exe-ctr-001)       =    zero and
                     rf-ybo-tbe-psc
                    (w-exe-ctr-001)       =    zero
                     go to exe-exp-ybx-620.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
